subSubSection.paragraph:
Colour
. In life, smaller specimens have a darker brown carapace with purple chelae and yellowish fingers (
Fig. 56F, G
). Larger specimens have carapaces which are lighter brown, with the chelae purplish-red to yellow (
Rademacher & Mengedoht, 2011: 29
) (see also 
Ng & Schubart, 2017
).
